title: Shyvana building AD/tank does as much AP damage as  lissandra??????

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
Shyvana's AP power is ridiculous
 https://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/251376737/202212098?tab=overview

In this game she alone is 1.7k damage from 2 Dragon's Breath to me with only a large Rod at one stage. 
When going bruiser shes almost unkillable if she gets a lead and goes tanky.

replies.body: because she lived long enough and the Liss was bad maybe + upgrade points can be stacked or not put an ability at all depending on the situations of the match
